advancedcompass.config.gui.showmode.tt.4: MAIN_HAND - show compass only if you have vanilla compass in your main hand
advancedcompass.config.gui.showmode.tt.5: BOTH_HANDS - show compass only if you have vanilla compass in your main or off hand
advancedcompass.config.gui.showmode.tt.6: ANY_SLOT - show compass only if you have vanilla compass anywhere in your inventory
advancedcompass.config.gui.coordmode.tt: Turn on/off coordinates above or below compass
advancedcompass.config.gui.yoff.tt: Offset from top of the screen (from 0 to 50)
advancedcompass.config.gui.maxrad.tt: Maximum distance from entity to player to show entity icon (from 0 to 999)
advancedcompass.config.gui.grouprad.tt: Maximum distance between entities to merge them into group (from 5 to 15)
advancedcompass.config.gui.viewan.tt: Angle of view that fits into the compass (from 30 to 360)
advancedcompass.config.gui.angletr.tt: Maximum angle between entity and player to render icon (from 15 to 180)
advancedcompass.config.gui.angletr_wp.tt: Maximum angle between waypoint and player to render icon (from 15 to 180)
advancedcompass.config.gui.hidebehind.tt: Hide mob icons if they are behind blocks
advancedcompass.config.gui.moveboss.tt: Move vanilla bossbar below the compass
advancedcompass.config.gui.overlapthresh: Overlap in pixels to hide overlapped icon (from 0 to 10)
advancedcompass.config.gui.moddedwp.tt.1: Way to show waypoints from other mods.
advancedcompass.config.gui.moddedwp.tt.2: SHOW_ENABLED - show only enabled in other mods waypoints
advancedcompass.config.gui.moddedwp.tt.3: SHOW_DISABLE - show only disabled in other mods waypoints
advancedcompass.config.gui.moddedwp.tt.4: SHOW_ALL - show all waypoints from other mods
advancedcompass.config.gui.moddedwp.tt.5: HIDE_ALL - hide all waypoints from other mods
advancedcompass.config.gui.generationtyp: HEAD_FIRST - mod will try to generate head icon first, if this is impossible it will generate full body icon and if even this is impossible it will use default icon.
FULL_BODY - mod will try to generate full body icon, if this is impossible it will use default icon.
OFF - default icons, zombie head for hostile and pig head for neutral mobs. (Only for modded mobs)
advancedcompass.waypoints.exists.1: Waypoint with this name already exists
advancedcompass.waypoints.exists.2: Press "Save" again to override it or change the name
advancedcompass.waypoints.empty: Can't create waypoint with empty name!
advancedcompass.waypoint.name: Name:
advancedcompass.waypoint.distance.tt: Minimum and maximum distance where waypoint will render (Max = 0 means there is no maximum and it will render in any distance above minimum)
